data.description: Acquire this well-maintained single-family home featuring 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, a private driveway, garage, and backyard, all within a convenient proximity to the Verrazzano Bridge.    The main level encompasses a roomy living room-dining room, a half bath, and a generously renovated eat-in kitchen with entry to an expansive garden. On the second floor, discover three large bedrooms complemented by a full bath. The finished basement comes equipped with an additional full bath. Complete with a garage and private driveway.    Call today for a showing!! Won't last!!!
